Step.SQLStatement: DROP VIEW LMX_CONCEPTOS; CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW LMX_CONCEPTOS AS SELECT 'es_MX' AS AD_Language, il.ad_client_id, il.ad_org_id, il.c_invoice_id, il.c_invoiceline_id, il.linenetamt AS conceptoimporte, il.qtyinvoiced AS conceptocantidad, TO_CHAR(il.priceactual, '99999999990.99') AS conceptovalorunitario, (SELECT c_uom_trl.uomsymbol FROM c_uom_trl WHERE c_uom_trl.ad_language = 'es_MX' AND c_uom_trl.c_uom_id = il.c_uom_id ) AS conceptounidad, COALESCE(p.name, il.description , ch.name ) AS conceptodescription, CASE WHEN il.M_Product_ID IS NOT NULL THEN p.value ELSE ch.name END AS conceptonoidentificacion, -- cfdi v3.3 tt.value AS conceptoClaveProdServ, (SELECT c_uom_trl.description FROM c_uom_trl WHERE c_uom_trl.ad_language = 'es_MX' AND c_uom_trl.c_uom_id = il.c_uom_id ) AS conceptoClaveUnidad FROM c_invoiceline il LEFT JOIN c_invoice i ON i.c_invoice_id = il.c_invoice_id LEFT JOIN c_bpartner bp ON bp.c_bpartner_id = i.c_bpartner_id LEFT JOIN c_bpartner_product bpp ON bpp.c_bpartner_id = bp.c_bpartner_id AND bpp.m_product_id = il.m_product_id LEFT JOIN m_product p ON p.m_product_id = il.m_product_id LEFT JOIN c_charge ch ON (ch.c_charge_id = il.c_charge_id) LEFT JOIN c_uom uom ON uom.c_uom_id = p.c_uom_id LEFT JOIN m_attributesetinstance ai ON ai.m_attributesetinstance_id = p.m_attributesetinstance_id LEFT JOIN c_taxtype tt ON tt.c_taxtype_id=p.c_taxtype_id;

Step.SQLStatement: CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW LMX_ConceptosTraslados AS SELECT 'es_MX' AS AD_Language, il.ad_client_id, il.ad_org_id, il.c_invoice_id, il.c_invoiceline_id, il.linenetamt AS ConceptoBase, impuesto AS ConceptoImpuesto, ( SELECT ad_ref_list_trl.name FROM ad_ref_list_trl WHERE ad_ref_list_trl.ad_language::text = 'es_MX' AND ad_ref_list_trl.ad_ref_list_id IN ( SELECT rl.ad_ref_list_id FROM ad_ref_list rl inner join ad_reference r on r.ad_reference_id=rl.ad_reference_id WHERE r.name='LMX_TipoFactor' AND rl.value::bpchar = tr.TipoFactor) ) AS ConceptTipoFactor, TO_CHAR(tr.tasaocuota,'00.00') AS ConceptoTasaOCuota, il.taxamt AS ConceptoImporte FROM c_invoiceline il LEFT JOIN c_invoice i ON i.c_invoice_id = il.c_invoice_id LEFT JOIN c_tax t ON t.c_tax_id = il.c_tax_id LEFT JOIN lmx_taxrate tr ON tr.c_tax_id = tr.c_tax_id ;

DROP VIEW LMX_RETENCIONES ; CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW LMX_RETENCIONES AS SELECT t.AD_Client_ID , it.AD_Org_ID, it.C_Invoice_ID , to_char(it.taxamt,'9999999990.99') AS RetencionImporte, -- trim(t.taxindicator) as Retencionimpuesto -- cfdi v3.3 tr.impuesto AS RetencionImpuesto, TO_CHAR(tr.tasaocuota, '9999999990.99') AS RetencionTasaOCuota, ( SELECT name FROM ad_ref_list_trl rl_trl WHERE rl_trl.ad_language = 'es_MX' AND rl_trl.ad_ref_list_id IN ( SELECT rl.ad_ref_list_id FROM ad_ref_list rl INNER JOIN ad_reference r on r.ad_reference_id=rl.ad_reference_id WHERE r.name='LMX_TipoFactor' AND rl.value = tr.TipoFactor) ) AS RetencionTipoFactor FROM C_InvoiceTax it INNER JOIN C_Tax t on t.C_Tax_ID=it.C_Tax_ID AND t.rate < 0 JOIN LMX_TaxRate tr ON tr.C_Tax_ID = tr.C_Tax_ID ;

DROP VIEW LMX_TRASLADOS ; CREATE OR REPLACE VIEW LMX_TRASLADOS AS SELECT it.AD_Client_ID , it.AD_Org_ID, it.C_Invoice_ID, TO_CHAR(it.taxamt,'99999999990.99') AS Trasladoimporte, -- it.C_Tax_ID as C_Tax_ID,trim(t.taxindicator) AS Trasladoimpuesto, -- remove CFDI v3.3 TO_CHAR(t.rate,'90.99') AS TrasladoTasa, --CFDI v3.3 tr.impuesto AS TrasladoImpuesto, TO_CHAR(tr.tasaocuota, '99999999.99') AS TrasladoTasaOCuota, ( SELECT name FROM AD_Ref_List_Trl rl_trl WHERE rl_trl.AD_Language = 'es_MX' AND rl_trl.AD_Ref_List_ID IN ( SELECT rl.AD_Ref_List_ID FROM AD_Ref_List rl INNER JOIN AD_reference r on r.AD_Reference_ID=rl.AD_Reference_ID WHERE r.name='LMX_TipoFactor' AND rl.value = tr.TipoFactor) ) AS TrasladoTipoFactor FROM C_InvoiceTax it INNER JOIN C_Tax t on t.C_Tax_ID=it.C_Tax_ID and t.rate >= 0 JOIN LMX_TaxRate tr ON tr.C_Tax_ID = tr.C_Tax_ID ;

A Client is a company or a legal entity. You cannot share data between Clients. Tenant is a synonym for Client.
An organization is a unit of your client or legal entity - examples are store, department. You can share data between organizations.
The record is active in the system

There are two methods of making records unavailable in the system: One is to delete the record, the other is to de-activate the record. A de-activated record is not available for selection, but available for reports. There are two reasons for de-activating and not deleting records: (1) The system requires the record for audit purposes. (2) The record is referenced by other records. E.g., you cannot delete a Business Partner, if there are invoices for this partner record existing. You de-activate the Business Partner and prevent that this record is used for future entries.
The Created field indicates the date that this record was created.
The Updated field indicates the date that this record was updated.
The Created By field indicates the user who created this record.
The Updated By field indicates the user who updated this record.
